-- Switchblade --

"The Predacons the most powerful faction in a war for dominance of 
this world among other things." Switchblade smiles.

"As for seeing Megatron, he's out leading an attack force to an 
enemy base. We were attacked not long ago, and he's paying them 
back." Switchblade motions for Tyrant to follow, and he starts 
heading out the transport ship.

Then he remembers Phoenix, "PHOENIX," he yells back at the other bot 
who was still in the exit of the base, "FOLLOW US."
